title: Ep. 50 - We Broke Into MrBeast's Studio (ft. MrBeast)
description: This week, the boys are joined by MrBeast himself inside his mega-studio in North Carolina. Topics include sleeping where he works, leaking his upcoming projects, and Ludwig convinces MrBeast to let him upload one of his videos on his own channel.
